WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:04.000
♪ ♪

00:08.000 --> 00:09.625
COLLEEN:
<i>Hi!</i>

00:09.709 --> 00:12.166
Thank you for watching Lark.
It's so nice we can

00:12.250 --> 00:13.500
