00:21.291 --> 00:22.959
Now I'm pretty.

00:23.041 --> 00:26.208
Wha... But-but you're also
pretty in your brain, too.

00:26.291 --> 00:28.583
Right? Where it,
where it really matters.

00:28.667 --> 00:30.333
(chuckles)

00:30.417 --> 00:33.500
Lark found one of my old pageant
gowns I had stored in the attic.

00:33.583 --> 00:35.208
What-what was Lark
doing in the attic?

00:35.291 --> 00:37.375
