04:05.834 --> 04:07.959
No, it's not fine. Okay?

04:08.041 --> 04:09.875
I'm her mother,
and it's not up to you.

04:09.959 --> 04:12.000
-So you and Matt can do this
to your own daughter.
-Oh...

04:13.542 --> 04:15.000
Hmm.

04:15.083 --> 04:16.542
I, uh, I-I'm sorry.

04:16.625 --> 04:18.041
I didn't, I didn't mean to...

04:18.125 --> 04:20.166
No, no, no.
It's fine. It's okay.

04:20.250 --> 04:22.625
Come on, Lark. We got to get you
in a warm bath for an hour

04:22.709 --> 04:24.041
