hang out with her.

04:55.166 --> 04:57.250
Aw. It's a Radisson basement.

04:57.333 --> 04:59.083
-Okay.
-And I love her so much.

04:59.166 --> 05:00.917
Well, you can play with her
anytime you want.

05:01.000 --> 05:02.709
I just hate that
she's never gonna get to do

05:02.792 --> 05:04.709
the routine we practiced.

05:04.792 --> 05:06.125
(sighs)

05:06.208 --> 05:07.250
Yep.

05:07.333 --> 05:10.291
Well, them's the breaks.

05:10.375 --> 05:11.375
-(both chuckle)
-I guess.

05:11.458 --> 05:13.291
-Good lesson for her, you know.
-Uh-huh.

05:13.375 --> 05:15.875
That you work hard at things and
sometimes they don't pay off.

05:15.959 --> 05:18.458
She just got so good at it.

05:18.542 --> 05:20.792
Yeah, yeah. She's a little
Renaissance toddler. So...

05:20.875 --> 05:22.041
And that baton
was super expensive.

05:22.125 --> 05:23.208
