05:23.291 --> 05:24.625
-Mm-hmm.
-...which cost even more.

05:24.709 --> 05:25.875
I don't know what
their return policy is,

05:25.959 --> 05:26.959
-so then, I'm just like, out...
-Okay.

05:27.041 --> 05:29.041
-Okay, fine. You win.
-...that cash.

05:29.125 --> 05:30.917
-(giggles)
-But I am her manager,

05:31.000 --> 05:33.750
