05:35.333 --> 05:36.667
Okay. Now,

05:36.750 --> 05:38.208
before we get started,

05:38.291 --> 05:40.083
just a reminder:

05:40.166 --> 05:42.083
do not look directly at Lark.

05:42.166 --> 05:46.208
Because you are about
to see a star. (giggles)

05:46.291 --> 05:48.875
