06:30.375 --> 06:32.875
Oh, dear God,
I hope we have a boy.

06:32.959 --> 06:35.125
Oh, boys can do pageants, too.

06:35.208 --> 06:36.959
♪ <i>Sweet sensation. </i>♪

06:39.000 --> 06:41.000
-Yay!
-Yes. Yes.

06:41.083 --> 06:42.208
-Yeah, baby.
-Yay!

06:42.291 --> 06:44.125
I did it!

06:47.500 --> 06:49.250
It was a beach cruiser

06:49.333 --> 06:51.083
with a wicker basket--
it was right there

06:51.166 --> 06:52.875
in the driveway,
then it was gone.

06:52.959 --> 06:55.750
You know, it's such
a violation to be robbed.

06:55.834 --> 06:57.875
It was a gift
from my husband.

06:57.959 --> 06:59.291
Don't you want
to write this down?

06:59.375 --> 07:00.875
Ma'am, I worked
at Fuddruckers for five years.

07:00.959 --> 07:02.625
I don't need to write it down.

07:02.709 --> 07:05.583
Right, okay, well then, dust
for prints, call for backup.

07:05.667 --> 07:08.250
I just need to know
that when bad things happen,

07:08.333 --> 07:12.000
somebody will step up
and do what's good.

07:12.083 --> 07:14.375
Ma'am, I believe what
you're describing is Batman.

07:14.458 --> 07:17.166
Oh, well, then call him.

07:17.250 --> 07:20.375
That cop couldn't have
cared less about my bike.

07:20.458 --> 07:24.000
She just gave up and then moved
on to some missing persons case.

07:24.083 --> 07:26.375
All right.
Let's find it on Craigslist.

07:26.458 --> 07:28.709
-(sighs)
-How would a robber

07:28.792 --> 07:30.542
describe your bike?

07:30.625 --> 07:31.750
Like a sunset

07:31.834 --> 07:34.291
after a week of rain.

07:34.375 --> 07:36.667
It had a kind of energy
to it.

07:36.750 --> 07:38.875
-So we'll say pink.
-Perfect.

07:38.959 --> 07:40.542
Okay, so you're gonna type in
the description here,

07:40.625 --> 07:42.166
and then you're gonna hit
the search button

07:42.250 --> 07:45.125
and it'll show you all the bikes
for sale in the area.

07:46.458 --> 07:49.625
Oh. There's nothing there.

07:49.709 --> 07:52.083
