07:52.166 --> 07:54.667
Oh, I thought you were telling
the computer to do that.

07:54.750 --> 07:56.917
No, no, <i>you </i>have to hit
the search button.

07:57.000 --> 08:00.208
-Oh!
-(chuckles)

08:00.291 --> 08:02.041
Still nothing.

08:02.125 --> 08:04.667
Mom, you didn't type anything;
you just hit the search button.

08:04.750 --> 08:06.750
Yeah, that's what you said
to do.

08:09.917 --> 08:11.792
Since when does this qualify
as brunch?

08:11.875 --> 08:13.250
This is the third
most disappointing spread

08:13.333 --> 08:14.375
