10:49.083 --> 10:50.125
Yeah. You win.

10:50.208 --> 10:51.208
Wait.

10:51.291 --> 10:53.333
If the reason you guys forgot me

10:53.417 --> 10:55.041
is 'cause you were stopping
to get gas,

10:55.125 --> 10:56.166
then why did we stop for gas?

10:56.250 --> 10:58.208
Tim, you are being paranoid,
okay?

10:58.291 --> 11:00.667
We did not leave you
at home intentionally.

11:00.750 --> 11:02.583
I never said intentionally.

11:02.667 --> 11:03.917
Will you take $80 for it?

11:04.000 --> 11:06.083
I'll go ask my friend.

11:09.083 --> 11:11.125
-Take the bike.
-What?

11:11.208 --> 11:13.208
Take the bike,
we don't have much time.

11:13.291 --> 11:14.333
You want us to steal it?

11:14.417 --> 11:16.291
It's not stealing, it's mine!

11:16.375 --> 11:18.375
Go!

11:18.458 --> 11:20.542
Let's go, let's go,
let's go, let's go.

11:20.625 --> 11:23.125
Oh, wow!
I haven't felt this high

11:23.208 --> 11:25.709
since the marijuana jam!

11:25.792 --> 11:27.625
-(chuckling)
-Where's Tim?

11:27.709 --> 11:30.125
What? We forgot Tim!

11:30.208 --> 11:31.417
(groans)

11:31.500 --> 11:33.375
Thanks for letting me
use your phone.

11:33.458 --> 11:34.625
I'm sure they're
just getting gas.

11:34.709 --> 11:36.208
-(line ringing)
-It's ringing.

11:36.291 --> 11:39.542
Tell them to bring my $80
or they don't get <i>you </i>back.

11:39.625 --> 11:41.625
Yeah, I think you're gonna need
a different approach.

