<i>to say good-bye... </i>♪

13:13.750 --> 13:14.709
(laughs)

13:14.792 --> 13:18.000
♪ ♪

13:18.083 --> 13:21.000
♪ <i>You and me go way back </i>♪

13:21.083 --> 13:24.083
♪ <i>It was the first trip</i>
<i>to the zoo </i>♪

13:24.166 --> 13:28.583
♪ <i>I remember it well, walking</i>
<i>hand in hand with you </i>♪

13:30.625 --> 13:32.542
♪ <i>We saw zebras </i>♪

13:32.625 --> 13:33.875
♪ <i>Birds in a nest </i>♪

13:33.959 --> 13:37.250
♪ <i>A divorcée dad</i>
<i>just doing his best </i>♪

13:37.333 --> 13:41.667
♪ <i>The zoo was such a sad</i>
<i>and boring place </i>♪

13:41.750 --> 13:44.375
♪ <i>Till that gator bit off</i>
<i>some guy's face </i>♪

13:44.458 --> 13:46.083
♪ <i>Now he's a millionaire </i>♪

13:46.166 --> 13:48.834
♪ <i>But, Mom, can't you see </i>♪

13:48.917 --> 13:49.875
Sophia.

13:49.959 --> 13:51.583
♪ <i>Each one holds a memory </i>♪

13:51.667 --> 13:52.834
I know, but...

13:52.917 --> 13:55.917
♪ <i>I'm not ready</i>
<i>to say good-bye </i>♪

13:56.000 --> 13:59.041
♪ <i>Ah, da-da, da-da-da-da </i>♪

13:59.125 --> 14:02.792
♪ <i>We're not ready</i>
<i>to say good-bye </i>♪

14:02.875 --> 14:03.959
No way, they can't stay.

14:04.041 --> 14:05.417
Please don't throw them away.

14:05.500 --> 14:07.709
♪ <i>Oh, please don't make us</i>
<i>have to leave </i>♪

14:07.792 --> 14:09.041
♪ <i>Oh, I've been in your toilet </i>♪

14:09.125 --> 14:11.834
♪ <i>I deserve a reprieve </i>♪

