♪ <i>We're not ready</i>
<i>to say good-bye. </i>♪

14:30.959 --> 14:32.667
No, no, no.

14:32.750 --> 14:34.125
Oh, One-Eyed Bear.

14:34.208 --> 14:36.041
♪ <i>I remember that one night </i>♪

14:36.125 --> 14:38.667
♪ <i>When Sophia left you</i>
<i>in my bed. </i>♪

14:38.750 --> 14:40.500
And I was there.

14:40.583 --> 14:42.500
♪ <i>When Tim bought you a purse </i>♪

14:42.583 --> 14:43.959
♪ <i>And you promised</i>
<i>to give him... </i>♪

14:44.041 --> 14:45.000
Yeah. Mm-hmm.

14:45.083 --> 14:46.917
That's why I ripped my eye out.

14:47.000 --> 14:48.792
Maybe we'll just
throw this guy out. Hmm?

14:48.875 --> 14:50.667
-What-what? No. Stop.
-♪ <i>And now it's time </i>♪

14:50.750 --> 14:52.917
-♪ <i>To say good-bye. </i>♪
-Mom, you can't. Mom!

14:53.000 --> 14:54.417
Where's Mr. Pickle?

14:54.500 --> 14:56.792
Sophia, you have enough already.

14:56.875 --> 14:58.834
But, Mom, I need him.

14:58.917 --> 15:01.792
Why? Why do you need
a talking pickle?

15:01.875 --> 15:03.834
(shouts, laughs)

15:06.333 --> 15:08.834
♪ <i>'Cause he's my best friend </i>♪

15:08.917 --> 15:11.542
♪ <i>Okay, technically</i>
<i>my boyfriend </i>♪

15:11.625 --> 15:13.667
♪ <i>Yeah, we stay up all night </i>♪

15:13.750 --> 15:15.125
♪ <i>It's nuts </i>♪

15:15.208 --> 15:17.917
♪ <i>Get on the iPad</i>
